name: Taiga Jira Importer

snapshot.content: Goal of this project is to build an importer into taiga from jira and vice versa. Nothing as this exists now. I need to change datatypes. Jira is xml and taiga is json. Will be comparing both these projects and may post the files here. Plan to use python to convert.
